{"title":"为Hexo添加数学公式渲染","uid":"fcd45286c67fb12e90ca4d87dc28e534","slug":"为Hexo添加数学公式渲染","date":"2025-05-09T08:00:00.000Z","updated":"2025-05-26T13:32:04.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/为Hexo添加数学公式渲染.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.luogu.com.cn/upload/image_hosting/fv11znvo.png","content":"<p>首先，删除渲染器，太菜了。</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki github-light\" style=\"background-color:#fff;color:#24292e\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1\">npm</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> un</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> hexo-renderer-marked</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5\"> --save</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>接下来就看你用什么渲染方式了。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>用 <code>mathjax</code>：（不推荐）</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki github-light\" style=\"background-color:#fff;color:#24292e\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1\">  npm</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> i</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> hexo-renderer-kramed</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5\"> --save</span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>用 <code>Katex</code>：（强烈推荐）</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki github-light\" style=\"background-color:#fff;color:#24292e\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1\">  npm</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> i</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> hexo-renderer-markdown-it-katex</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5\"> --save</span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">Update 2025&#x2F;5&#x2F;26 注意</p>\n<p>据说 mathjax 很慢，尽量使用 Katex。</p>\n\n</div>\n<p>那个 <code>@upupming/hexo-renderer-markdown-it-plus</code> 不好用，<code>hexo-renderer-markdown-it-plus</code>  已经停止维护了。</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">Update 2025&#x2F;5&#x2F;26 危险！！！</p>\n<p><p>如果你用的不是 <code>hljs</code> 高亮，你就不能用这种方法！替代方法请看下面。</p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"Update-2025-5-26-新方法，适合不使用-hljs-的博主\"><a href=\"#Update-2025-5-26-新方法，适合不使用-hljs-的博主\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Update 2025&#x2F;5&#x2F;26 新方法，适合不使用 hljs 的博主\"></a>Update 2025&#x2F;5&#x2F;26 新方法，适合不使用 hljs 的博主</h2><p>首先：</p>\n<p>根据需要选择：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki github-light\" style=\"background-color:#fff;color:#24292e\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1\">npm</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> i</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> hexo-filter-katex</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"shiki github-light\" style=\"background-color:#fff;color:#24292e\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1\">npm</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> i</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> hexo-filter-mathjax</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>然后，在 <code>_config.yml</code> 添加如下字段：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki github-light\" style=\"background-color:#fff;color:#24292e\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#22863A\">math</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#22863A\">  every_page</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">: </span><span style=\"color:#005CC5\">true</span><span style=\"color:#6A737D\"> # 是否每个页面都渲染，bool</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#22863A\">  mathjax</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#22863A\">    enable</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">: </span><span style=\"color:#005CC5\">false</span><span style=\"color:#6A737D\"> # 是否启用</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A737D\">    # 三种值: none | ams | all</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#22863A\">    tags</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">: </span><span style=\"color:#032F62\">none</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#22863A\">  katex</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#22863A\">    enable</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">: </span><span style=\"color:#005CC5\">true</span><span style=\"color:#6A737D\"> # 是否启用</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A737D\">    # 复制 Katex 源码，可以去 https://github.com/KaTeX/KaTeX/tree/master/contrib/copy-tex 看</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A737D\">    # 但 Aurora 主题好像用不了</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#22863A\">    copy_tex</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">: </span><span style=\"color:#005CC5\">true</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>再：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki github-light\" style=\"background-color:#fff;color:#24292e\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1\">hexo</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> cl</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\"> &#x26;&#x26; </span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1\">hexo</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\"> g</span></span></code></pre>\n\n","text":"首先，删除渲染器，太菜了。 npm un hexo-renderer-marked --save 接下来就看你用什么渲染方式了。 用 mathjax：（不推荐）...","permalink":"/post/为Hexo添加数学公式渲染","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":864,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"},{"name":"博客相关","slug":"博客相关","count":3,"path":"api/tags/博客相关.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Update-2025-5-26-%E6%96%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-hljs-%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E4%B8%BB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Update 2025&#x2F;5&#x2F;26 新方法，适合不使用 hljs 的博主</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CodeNebula","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.luogu.com.cn/upload/image_hosting/dsfhfazq.png","link":"/","description":"Take a tour of 『CodeNebula』| 在『代码星云』里遨游。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/zhangyimin12345","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"Hexo主题安装","uid":"5326e1446e1cb298bfb0d2f63b3a53dc","slug":"Hexo主题安装","date":"2025-05-09T08:00:00.000Z","updated":"2025-05-26T13:21:12.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo主题安装.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.luogu.com.cn/upload/image_hosting/fv11znvo.png","te